<p>Dave, John, and your fellow Mac Geek Gab listeners have TONS of tips to share today. Highlights include managing Lion&rsquo;s resume, dealing with Apple Customer Relations (versus AppleCare), what to do to ensure a successful clean Lion install, fixing missing icons in your Dock, and flashing your new iMac&rsquo;s DVD drive to ensure full ripping speed. All this and more in today&rsquo;s (free!) episode of Mac Geek Gab. Download and enjoy!</p>
